These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: brazilian, polish, malaysian, russian, colombian, australian, american
1. the polish is in the middle##1
2. the polish is on the left of the malaysian##1
3. the colombian is on the right of the russian##1
4. the brazilian is on the right of the malaysian##1
5. the american is on the far left##1
6. the australian is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Nationality   | american | russian | colombian | polish | malaysian | brazilian | australian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  bartender, videographer, police-officer, journalist, scientist, musician, freelancer
1. the freelancer is on the far right##1
2. the bartender is on the far left##1
3. the bartender is on the left of the scientist##1
4. the scientist is on the left of the police-officer##1
5. the journalist is on the right of the musician##1
6. the freelancer is on the right of the videographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Job   | bartender | scientist | police-officer | musician | journalist | videographer | freelancer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: baking, collecting, writing, chess, cooking, traveling, dancing
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby   | cooking | baking | traveling | writing | dancing | collecting | chess |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-4::.
