.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-5::.
7 different pets are kept: hamster, rat, fish, bird, goat, rabbit, horse
1. the owner of the rabbit is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
4. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
5. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2     |   3    |   4   |    5     |     6      |   7   |
| Pet   | horse | fish | bird | rabbit | hamster | rat | goat |

